{"tid":12572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為期6日打擊違泊行動結束 共發出3萬張定額罰款書","createTime":"2016-11-29T17:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T17:23:59.000Z","uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d26229f3e2dd0fe12dcd2a76b839116fd481ec6f","tid":12572,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:08:39.000Z","msg":"警方結束為期6日的打擊違例泊車等行動，共拖走40輛車﹐發<span style=\"color: red;\">出超過3萬張定額罰款通知書</span>。警方表示會繼續嚴厲執法，打擊違例泊車。<br />\n警方表示，今次是今年第4次打擊非法泊車的行動，警方在今年1至9月間，共發出116萬張違例泊車的定額罰款通知書，比2015年同期發出的超過96萬張，升21%。<br />\n<br />\n香港電台<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322c7adbcd555c6cf170f9877466f4b2deafa591","tid":12572,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:09:56.000Z","msg":"庫房又多1000萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca22fbb5a0b17e0b474fd693b73ddc5cf1a61c91","tid":12572,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:23:59.000Z","msg":"又交到數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}